title: Camp WeWow Bug Week Day 3
description:
It's Weather Week at Camp WeWow! Today, we're making snail snacks!! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/recipe-snail-snacks for directions to today's activity and share what you're tinkering with at tinkercast.com/share! Do you have a creepy crawler bug story?! Call us at 1-888-7WOW-WOW to share your 60 second bug story! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire this Friday!
